WEBVTT

01:24.400 --> 01:24.840
Here

01:24.840 --> 01:26.700
is the famous Malacca Chinatown.

01:27.240 --> 01:27.680
And

01:27.680 --> 01:29.000
for Malaysian Chinese,

01:29.000 --> 01:31.400
the most important day of the year is the New Year.

01:31.400 --> 01:32.600
So these decorations

01:32.640 --> 01:33.920
represent the Malaysian Chinese's

01:33.920 --> 01:35.380
love for Chinese culture.

01:37.080 --> 01:37.610
Let's go.

01:39.000 --> 01:39.530
Let's go.

02:28.320 --> 02:29.380
Do I really have to?

02:29.840 --> 02:30.520
Just try it.

02:31.320 --> 02:32.640
I'd rather not.

02:33.400 --> 02:35.079
Are you really not going to try it?

02:35.079 --> 02:35.480
No.

02:37.320 --> 02:39.680
I really can't get used to this smell.

02:40.440 --> 02:42.500
There's a first time for everything.

02:42.800 --> 02:43.480
Try it.

02:43.880 --> 02:44.480
Next time.

02:45.240 --> 02:45.840
Right now.

02:46.680 --> 02:47.200
Boss.

02:49.480 --> 02:49.810
Here.

02:59.640 --> 03:00.570
Thank you, boss.

03:08.640 --> 03:10.100
Do you really not want any?

03:10.320 --> 03:12.320
Look, even Justin doesn't want any.

03:12.440 --> 03:13.160
Justin,

03:14.600 --> 03:15.720
do you really not want any?

03:15.720 --> 03:17.320
Never mind. I don't want any.

03:18.280 --> 03:19.760
Aren't you Malaysian?

03:20.400 --> 03:20.960
Only in this regard,

03:20.960 --> 03:22.680
I am super un-Malaysian.

03:24.840 --> 03:25.360
See?

03:26.640 --> 03:27.240
All right.

03:37.560 --> 03:38.090
Try some.

03:46.920 --> 03:47.450
How is it?

03:53.040 --> 03:53.560
Not bad.

03:54.000 --> 03:55.530
It's better than I thought.

03:56.240 --> 03:56.960
Try this again.

03:56.960 --> 03:57.520
Again?

03:58.040 --> 03:59.240
Eat this piece. Here.

04:04.040 --> 04:05.640
How is it? Delicious, right?

04:06.000 --> 04:06.600
It's okay.

04:32.560 --> 04:33.480
I like it here.

04:40.159 --> 04:40.960
What's wrong?

04:55.320 --> 04:56.600
You could have told me.

04:56.920 --> 04:57.850
I'm fine with it.

04:58.520 --> 04:59.640
Tell you what?

05:01.840 --> 05:03.240
Mr. Zeng invited you here

05:04.800 --> 05:07.000
not just to help them repair porcelain.

05:08.320 --> 05:11.120
He also wants you to stay here as an exchange student.

05:11.120 --> 05:12.050
How did you know?

05:12.760 --> 05:14.760
There's more room for development here

05:14.760 --> 05:15.820
and a bigger stage.

05:17.880 --> 05:18.400
Even though

05:18.400 --> 05:20.660
we might not see each other for two years.

05:27.640 --> 05:28.680
But I believe

05:30.000 --> 05:31.930
as long as we still miss each other,

05:32.200 --> 05:34.260
this distance and time won't stop us.

05:40.360 --> 05:41.960
If you don't like me anymore,

05:43.000 --> 05:44.260
I respect your choice.

05:51.680 --> 05:53.200
As long as you choose

05:56.120 --> 05:57.360
the path you prefer.

06:01.440 --> 06:02.760
They all told me to be a bit selfish,

06:02.760 --> 06:03.840
think of myself,

06:05.640 --> 06:06.770
and ask you not to go.

06:08.840 --> 06:10.900
After thinking about it, I still feel

06:12.880 --> 06:14.480
I should respect your choice

06:15.560 --> 06:17.160
because it's your own life.

06:21.960 --> 06:23.560
But I don't want you to leave.

06:24.520 --> 06:26.520
When did I ever say I was leaving you?

06:26.920 --> 06:27.850
What did you say?

06:28.440 --> 06:30.240
I've already rejected Mr. Zeng.

06:30.400 --> 06:31.330
I won't stay here

06:31.840 --> 06:32.300
because

06:35.840 --> 06:36.840
without you here,

06:37.280 --> 06:38.800
there's no point in staying.

06:38.800 --> 06:40.200
What else are you asking?

06:47.120 --> 06:48.380
What else did they say?

06:50.360 --> 06:51.080
Nothing.

06:51.800 --> 06:54.060
There are scholarships and a stage here.

06:54.240 --> 06:56.000
From the very beginning, I felt...

06:56.000 --> 06:56.730
Without you,

06:57.400 --> 06:59.840
no matter how good the conditions or how big the stage,

06:59.840 --> 07:01.100
it means nothing to me.

07:05.400 --> 07:06.640
I won't stay alone in Malacca,

07:06.640 --> 07:07.700
a place so far away.

07:11.560 --> 07:13.560
What if someone else takes you away?

07:17.040 --> 07:18.900
What if you fall for someone else?

07:19.960 --> 07:21.090
Then what would I do?

07:23.280 --> 07:26.010
You've been talking to yourself this whole time.

07:27.000 --> 07:29.660
I don't need you to respect my choices like this.

07:30.880 --> 07:33.340
I just need you to need me, and that's enough.

07:39.720 --> 07:40.250
Xiaocen.

07:46.720 --> 07:47.720
I won't leave you.

07:51.680 --> 07:53.340
You will always be in my story.

08:27.680 --> 08:28.280
Xu,

08:29.000 --> 08:30.600
about the exchange program,

08:30.880 --> 08:33.080
are you really not going to reconsider?

08:35.679 --> 08:37.280
Thank you for your kindness.

08:37.400 --> 08:38.659
But I've still decided

08:38.960 --> 08:40.760
to stay and study in Jingdezhen.

08:47.600 --> 08:48.320
All right.

08:48.720 --> 08:50.520
Since you've made up your minds,

08:50.720 --> 08:52.120
I won't push it.

08:53.520 --> 08:54.160
Xu,

08:54.720 --> 08:55.250
Xiaocen,

08:56.840 --> 08:58.440
I want to show you something.

09:00.440 --> 09:00.920
Here.

09:04.040 --> 09:07.700
This is a blue-and-white porcelain vase from the Zhizheng reign.

09:07.880 --> 09:09.880
The decoration is of dragons in seawater.

09:09.880 --> 09:11.480
The color is rich and bright.

09:12.640 --> 09:13.770
If I'm not mistaken,

09:14.120 --> 09:14.920
this is a piece

09:15.240 --> 09:18.440
from the imperial kiln of Jingdezhen in the Yuan Dynasty.

09:20.560 --> 09:22.840
Blue-and-white porcelain from the Yuan Dynasty is very rare,

09:22.840 --> 09:24.900
let alone this one you have, Mr. Zeng.

09:25.160 --> 09:27.090
Although the body is a bit damaged,

09:27.440 --> 09:28.900
it is still very precious.

09:29.240 --> 09:30.320
To get it,

09:30.480 --> 09:32.360
I really went to a lot of trouble.

09:34.080 --> 09:34.640
Xu,

09:36.240 --> 09:37.320
can you complete

09:37.760 --> 09:38.680
the restoration of this porcelain?

09:38.680 --> 09:40.340
Given my current skill level,

09:40.800 --> 09:42.320
it would be quite difficult for me

09:42.320 --> 09:43.920
to restore this piece alone.

09:44.040 --> 09:45.440
I'd still need a more skilled restorer

09:45.440 --> 09:46.600
like Mr. Yue

09:46.600 --> 09:47.730
to help me finish it.

09:49.560 --> 09:50.640
I thought so too.

09:51.480 --> 09:53.080
Therefore, I've decided

09:53.600 --> 09:57.960
to donate this piece to Jingdezhen Ceramic University

09:58.880 --> 10:01.760
for your university to restore and collect.

10:03.720 --> 10:05.720
You want to donate such a valuable piece of porcelain

10:05.720 --> 10:06.520
to our school?

10:07.560 --> 10:10.090
This piece originally came from Jingdezhen.

10:10.320 --> 10:11.320
It ended up abroad

10:11.720 --> 10:13.160
because it was

10:13.160 --> 10:14.520
illegally salvaged.

10:15.240 --> 10:18.000
I'm just returning it to its rightful owner.

10:19.240 --> 10:20.200
But Mr. Zeng,

10:20.760 --> 10:22.320
you spent so much money and effort

10:22.320 --> 10:23.080
on this.

10:23.800 --> 10:25.800
Are you just going to donate it to us?

10:25.840 --> 10:28.320
I think returning to its homeland

10:28.440 --> 10:29.840
is its best destination.

10:30.440 --> 10:32.760
I used to worry that young people in China

10:32.760 --> 10:34.520
wouldn't value this cultural heritage.

10:34.520 --> 10:35.850
But seeing your passion

10:36.320 --> 10:39.320
and professionalism in cultural relics restoration

10:39.600 --> 10:40.460
has touched me.

10:40.880 --> 10:42.080
Knowing there are still young people like you

10:42.080 --> 10:44.040
in China

10:44.040 --> 10:45.970
inheriting traditional culture,

10:46.520 --> 10:47.520
I feel reassured.

10:48.240 --> 10:49.040
I believe

10:49.280 --> 10:51.010
you will take good care of them.

10:58.320 --> 10:58.920
Xu Xiao,

10:59.240 --> 10:59.800
Xiaocen.

11:00.120 --> 11:01.180
I won't see you out.

11:01.520 --> 11:03.760
Thank you for your hospitality during this time.

11:03.760 --> 11:04.680
You're welcome.

11:04.680 --> 11:06.940
You helped me restore so much porcelain.

11:07.040 --> 11:08.640
I should be the one thanking you.

11:08.640 --> 11:10.200
It was our honor, Mr. Zeng.

11:10.400 --> 11:11.600
Thank you for your hard work.

11:11.600 --> 11:13.440
As for the cultural relic I donated,

11:13.440 --> 11:15.040
I have entrusted a transport company

11:15.040 --> 11:16.640
to deliver it to Jingdezhen.

11:16.640 --> 11:18.440
Your school has already received it.

11:18.440 --> 11:20.520
I'll leave its restoration to you.

11:21.000 --> 11:21.360
Okay.

11:21.880 --> 11:23.480
Rest assured, leave it to us.

11:25.080 --> 11:26.600
We'll be taking our leave now.

11:26.600 --> 11:27.200
Thank you.

11:28.080 --> 11:28.440
Thank you.

11:28.440 --> 11:30.000
Please visit Malaysia again.

11:30.000 --> 11:31.260
Come visit us in China.

11:31.840 --> 11:32.200
Okay.

11:32.560 --> 11:33.690
We'll get going now.

11:33.920 --> 11:34.320
Bye.

11:34.440 --> 11:34.800
Bye.

11:34.840 --> 11:35.440
Bye.

11:35.480 --> 11:36.010
Goodbye.

11:36.280 --> 11:36.840
Bye.

11:39.400 --> 11:39.880
Bye.

11:40.160 --> 11:40.800
Bye.

11:41.320 --> 11:41.800
Bye.

12:02.600 --> 12:03.200
Xu Xiao.

12:04.840 --> 12:07.520
Mr. Zeng told me everything about you.

12:08.000 --> 12:10.000
He is very satisfied with your work.

12:10.440 --> 12:11.500
Thank you, Mr. Yue.

12:12.680 --> 12:13.760
And you, Xiaocen.

12:14.240 --> 12:16.970
I can't believe you went to Malaysia by yourself.

12:18.240 --> 12:19.840
Mr. Zeng is also

12:20.480 --> 12:22.210
very satisfied with your work.

12:22.400 --> 12:23.880
You impressed him.

12:24.600 --> 12:25.200
Really?

12:27.760 --> 12:28.400
Xu Xiao.

12:29.120 --> 12:31.240
I heard you gave up the opportunity

12:31.520 --> 12:32.980
to be an exchange student.

12:34.040 --> 12:35.370
I've disappointed you.

12:35.680 --> 12:36.280
Actually,

12:37.280 --> 12:39.640
I didn't want you to be an exchange student.

12:39.640 --> 12:40.840
Such a good prospect,

12:41.240 --> 12:43.700
who would want to let someone else teach you?

12:45.800 --> 12:46.400
By the way,

12:47.640 --> 12:49.800
The porcelain donated by Mr. Zeng

12:50.160 --> 12:50.890
has arrived.

12:51.240 --> 12:53.320
I checked its damage

12:53.560 --> 12:55.200
and made a restoration plan.

12:57.400 --> 12:58.040
Are you two

12:59.360 --> 13:00.690
interested in joining?

13:01.360 --> 13:02.040
Of course.

13:03.080 --> 13:03.560
Good.

13:04.240 --> 13:05.170
It's a deal then.

13:07.120 --> 13:07.720
However,

13:08.880 --> 13:11.080
the injury on my hand hasn't healed yet.

13:11.480 --> 13:13.740
I can't participate in the restoration.

13:15.080 --> 13:16.540
Mr. Yue, what should we do?

13:16.640 --> 13:17.600
It's nothing.

13:18.240 --> 13:19.170
You should know,

13:19.240 --> 13:20.100
in Jingdezhen,

13:20.760 --> 13:22.090
there is another expert

13:22.440 --> 13:23.640
who has a deeper study

13:24.320 --> 13:26.320
of blue-and-white porcelain.

13:47.400 --> 13:48.080
Xu.

13:53.080 --> 13:53.520
Xiao.

13:56.320 --> 13:56.920
Xu.

13:56.920 --> 13:58.200
Yue, long time no see.

13:59.160 --> 14:00.160
Long time no see.

14:01.240 --> 14:01.800
How is it?

14:02.480 --> 14:03.000
Come on.

14:03.600 --> 14:04.600
Let's have a look.

14:07.360 --> 14:08.160
By the way, Xu.

14:09.240 --> 14:11.040
The two young people I mentioned

14:11.280 --> 14:13.400
are Xu Xiao and Xiaocen.

14:18.840 --> 14:19.560
Dad,

14:19.840 --> 14:22.680
why do you use tea water to mix this pigment?

14:22.840 --> 14:24.560
When we mix the pigment,

14:24.560 --> 14:27.680
it's best to use tea water that's been sitting for about a week.

14:27.680 --> 14:28.880
Because at this time,

14:28.880 --> 14:31.000
the tea water can fully ferment.

14:31.160 --> 14:32.320
After fermentation,

14:32.320 --> 14:34.080
when the pigment mixes with water,

14:34.080 --> 14:35.740
it won't easily precipitate.

14:36.320 --> 14:38.840
And it can slow down the speed

14:38.840 --> 14:40.320
of it entering the surface of the body.

14:40.320 --> 14:42.880
It makes it easier for us to draw

14:42.880 --> 14:43.880
on the body later.

14:44.920 --> 14:46.920
Once we lay the foundation

14:47.080 --> 14:48.880
and finish outlining the lines,

14:49.040 --> 14:51.440
we will need to use a water-separating pen.

14:52.160 --> 14:54.490
Doesn't it look like a big rooster's beak?

14:55.120 --> 14:55.480
It does.

14:55.480 --> 14:57.720
This is called a chicken-head brush, got it?

14:57.720 --> 14:59.600
Then we use it for coloring.

14:59.920 --> 15:02.640
Dad, how do you know so much?

15:03.360 --> 15:04.920
Who do you think your dad is?

15:05.600 --> 15:07.480
When it comes to studying blue-and-white porcelain,

15:07.480 --> 15:10.160
I am the best in Jingdezhen.

15:10.880 --> 15:11.600
Dad.

15:11.760 --> 15:13.040
When I grow up,

15:13.040 --> 15:15.160
I want to be as amazing as you.

15:15.200 --> 15:16.930
You will definitely be like me.

15:17.320 --> 15:19.250
And you will do even better than me.

16:13.480 --> 16:14.140
Good night.

16:16.080 --> 16:16.740
Good night.

16:19.840 --> 16:20.360
I'm off.

16:22.760 --> 16:23.200
Bye.

16:34.800 --> 16:35.400
Old Xu,

16:36.360 --> 16:38.200
you've kept your skills sharp.

16:39.040 --> 16:40.760
You even keep up with the times.

16:40.760 --> 16:41.720
Good for you.

16:42.200 --> 16:43.200
To be honest,

16:43.520 --> 16:44.640
after all these years,

16:44.640 --> 16:45.800
I never dared

16:46.000 --> 16:47.560
to let my skills slip.

16:48.960 --> 16:49.600
Of course,

16:50.080 --> 16:52.280
it's mostly because of this kid.

16:53.000 --> 16:53.720
It was Xiao

16:54.280 --> 16:56.520
who pulled me back to a normal state.

16:58.600 --> 17:00.080
I want to state my position.

17:00.080 --> 17:02.080
In the future, whenever you need me,

17:02.480 --> 17:03.360
I am duty-bound

17:03.960 --> 17:05.690
and will definitely do my best.

17:05.720 --> 17:06.400
Lao Xu,

17:07.599 --> 17:09.930
isn't that why we asked you here this time?

17:10.200 --> 17:11.660
We wouldn't leave you out.

17:14.240 --> 17:14.839
Mr. Yue,

17:15.680 --> 17:16.560
does our school museum

17:16.560 --> 17:17.800
have a lot of

17:17.800 --> 17:18.760
precious porcelain like this?

17:18.760 --> 17:19.400
Yes.

17:19.920 --> 17:20.440
You see,

17:21.119 --> 17:24.079
this entire hall was donated by overseas Chinese.

17:25.240 --> 17:26.599
Don't underestimate

17:26.599 --> 17:28.240
every single piece of these cultural relics.

17:28.240 --> 17:29.520
These are all overseas Chinese.

17:29.520 --> 17:31.640
The bond connecting with the motherland.

17:31.640 --> 17:33.160
Behind every cultural relic

17:33.160 --> 17:35.160
lies the overseas Chinese's

17:35.360 --> 17:38.680
yearning and affection for their motherland and hometown.

17:38.680 --> 17:39.240
You

17:39.400 --> 17:41.920
will have many opportunities in the future to come into contact with

17:41.920 --> 17:42.980
and participate in

17:43.120 --> 17:45.160
this kind of restoration work.

17:45.880 --> 17:47.140
You must remember that

17:47.200 --> 17:48.360
every restoration

17:48.840 --> 17:51.370
It is the inheritance of culture and emotion.

17:51.720 --> 17:53.120
Every restoration

17:53.680 --> 17:55.320
connects history

17:56.200 --> 17:57.160
and the present.

18:10.560 --> 18:12.090
The holiday is almost over.

18:13.800 --> 18:14.640
And then?

18:15.760 --> 18:16.600
Then,

18:17.400 --> 18:18.530
I'll be a sophomore.

18:19.760 --> 18:20.720
And after that?

18:22.000 --> 18:22.800
After that,

18:25.760 --> 18:27.760
junior and senior years.

18:29.480 --> 18:30.210
Graduation.

18:31.000 --> 18:31.520
Work.

18:33.240 --> 18:34.040
Get married.

18:37.920 --> 18:38.520
Have kids.

18:43.440 --> 18:44.160
Retire.

18:45.800 --> 18:46.400
Pass away.

18:51.240 --> 18:52.720
Fired porcelain

18:54.520 --> 18:55.960
after a hundred

18:56.720 --> 18:57.850
or a thousand years,

18:59.840 --> 19:01.480
will remain the same.

19:05.840 --> 19:07.040
Tell me,

19:09.160 --> 19:11.160
where will we be in a thousand years?

19:19.520 --> 19:20.050
Xiaocen.

19:21.240 --> 19:22.170
All I know is that

19:23.240 --> 19:24.300
tomorrow morning,

19:24.760 --> 19:27.360
I will wait for you downstairs with breakfast.

19:28.360 --> 19:29.490
When school starts,

19:30.160 --> 19:31.420
I will see you in class.

19:33.080 --> 19:34.080
When we graduate,

19:35.080 --> 19:37.880
we will attend the graduation ceremony together.

19:39.440 --> 19:40.120
I hope

19:41.280 --> 19:42.240
in the important

19:42.720 --> 19:44.450
stages of your life from now on,

19:45.680 --> 19:47.280
I will always be by your side.

19:58.520 --> 19:59.640
I don't know where we will be

19:59.640 --> 20:00.770
in a thousand years.

20:09.080 --> 20:09.880
But right now,

20:11.400 --> 20:12.280
to me,

20:14.040 --> 20:14.900
it is eternity.

20:41.040 --> 20:43.970
Don't you think this pattern looks like ocean waves?

20:44.800 --> 20:46.920
This is a typical curved wave pattern,

20:46.920 --> 20:48.980
also known as the ocean wave pattern.

20:49.040 --> 20:49.840
I understand.

20:50.840 --> 20:53.440
You need to look at these more and compare.

20:53.440 --> 20:55.960
Once you've seen enough, your experience will improve.

20:55.960 --> 20:56.690
Understand?

20:56.920 --> 20:57.650
Understood.

20:59.120 --> 21:00.760
How is your mom doing lately?

21:02.480 --> 21:03.480
She's doing well.

21:03.760 --> 21:04.640
A while ago,

21:04.880 --> 21:07.240
she even went traveling to Zhangjiajie with Uncle Song.

21:07.240 --> 21:08.040
That's good.

21:10.280 --> 21:11.920
Now that you're growing up,

21:12.560 --> 21:14.600
you need to be more understanding of your mom.

21:14.600 --> 21:16.200
It's not easy for her either.

21:16.640 --> 21:18.440
In the past, it was all my fault.

21:19.960 --> 21:20.760
I let you down.

21:22.560 --> 21:23.520
But at least,

21:24.280 --> 21:24.940
seeing that

21:25.120 --> 21:26.580
your mom is doing well now,

21:27.120 --> 21:28.240
I feel relieved.

21:30.680 --> 21:31.280
By the way,

21:31.440 --> 21:33.480
if you ever have any problems

21:34.080 --> 21:35.400
at school in the future,

21:35.400 --> 21:36.320
just come to me.

21:36.480 --> 21:36.920
Okay.

21:37.080 --> 21:38.960
Let me tell you about Yue Qixin.

21:39.280 --> 21:40.160
His level

21:40.880 --> 21:42.840
can only be said to be so-so.

21:43.720 --> 21:44.720
But let me tell you,

21:44.720 --> 21:46.720
when it comes to blue-and-white porcelain,

21:46.720 --> 21:48.600
your dad is definitely the best.

21:48.920 --> 21:49.320
Yeah.

21:49.840 --> 21:50.300
Really.

21:50.440 --> 21:50.880
I know.

21:51.480 --> 21:51.940
Really.

21:51.960 --> 21:53.240
In the future, regarding blue-and-white porcelain...

21:53.240 --> 21:54.100
By the way, Dad,

21:54.600 --> 21:55.360
I have something to do.

21:55.360 --> 21:56.600
I still need to go to the antique shop.

21:56.600 --> 21:57.160
I suddenly remembered something.

21:57.160 --> 21:57.640
Okay.

21:57.960 --> 21:58.320
I'll get going then.

21:58.320 --> 21:59.080
Go ahead then.

21:59.080 --> 21:59.920
Oh, wait.

22:00.520 --> 22:01.850
Say hi to Xiaocen for me.

22:02.000 --> 22:02.530
Alright.

22:03.080 --> 22:03.680
Off you go.

22:03.800 --> 22:04.120
Bye.

22:04.920 --> 22:05.520
Come visit

22:07.320 --> 22:07.920
often.

22:08.320 --> 22:08.840
Got it.

22:09.840 --> 22:11.200
Mom, I'm all packed.

22:11.720 --> 22:13.920
Now, I'm officially preparing to live on campus

22:13.920 --> 22:15.320
and start my school life.

22:16.720 --> 22:18.000
After moving into the dorm,

22:18.000 --> 22:19.640
make sure to eat fruit every day.

22:19.640 --> 22:21.720
Don't stay up late. Go to bed early.

22:21.720 --> 22:23.360
Staying up late is terrible for your health.

22:23.360 --> 22:24.220
Remember that.

22:24.440 --> 22:25.400
Got it.

22:26.200 --> 22:27.200
Think about it again.

22:27.200 --> 22:28.880
Is there anything you need Mom

22:28.880 --> 22:29.800
to send you from home?

22:29.800 --> 22:31.360
I... I don't need anything.

22:31.360 --> 22:32.600
I brought everything.

22:32.600 --> 22:34.360
Don't leave things behind.

22:34.960 --> 22:35.560
Got it.

22:36.360 --> 22:36.920
Is it heavy?

22:36.920 --> 22:38.240
It's not heavy.

22:39.440 --> 22:40.570
I'm really worried.

22:41.800 --> 22:42.800
I'm leaving, Mom.

22:43.320 --> 22:44.080
Cencen.

22:44.280 --> 22:45.560
Maybe you shouldn't move into

22:45.560 --> 22:46.640
the school dorm.

22:46.760 --> 22:48.240
Just stay at your aunt's house.

22:48.240 --> 22:49.800
Or I can go there tomorrow.

22:50.520 --> 22:51.120
Sister.

22:51.120 --> 22:52.920
Qingying, I'll go over tomorrow.

22:52.920 --> 22:53.880
No need.

22:54.360 --> 22:55.400
As for Xiaocen's room,

22:55.400 --> 22:56.600
I'm keeping it for her.

22:56.600 --> 22:57.680
She can come back

22:57.680 --> 22:58.680
whenever she wants.

22:58.680 --> 22:59.680
Whatever she wants to eat,

22:59.680 --> 23:00.810
I'll make it for her.

23:00.840 --> 23:01.720
So don't worry.

23:01.800 --> 23:03.200
Growing up,

23:03.360 --> 23:05.720
this is her first time living alone away from me.

23:05.720 --> 23:06.640
I'm worried.

23:06.640 --> 23:08.360
Xiaocen is a big girl now.

23:08.360 --> 23:09.960
She can take care of herself.

23:10.120 --> 23:11.120
If you

23:11.760 --> 23:13.360
have time, you can stay here anytime.

23:13.360 --> 23:15.520
Mom, stop worrying.

23:15.800 --> 23:17.040
Okay.

23:17.040 --> 23:19.170
As long as you take care of yourselves,

23:19.200 --> 23:20.000
I'll be relieved.

23:20.000 --> 23:22.060
You need to take care of yourself too.

23:23.240 --> 23:24.640
Take care of your health.

23:25.160 --> 23:26.640
By the way, if anything happens,

23:26.640 --> 23:28.240
call me immediately.

23:28.240 --> 23:28.720
Okay.

23:29.040 --> 23:29.880
I'm hanging up now.

23:29.880 --> 23:30.680
Okay, bye.

23:30.840 --> 23:31.400
Bye.

23:31.400 --> 23:32.600
Okay, bye.

23:36.240 --> 23:37.000
Your mom

23:37.000 --> 23:38.800
still worries about you so much.

23:38.920 --> 23:39.760
Aunt.

23:39.920 --> 23:41.720
My mom won't change that easily.

23:41.720 --> 23:42.520
But

23:42.680 --> 23:44.810
I need to become less dependent on her.

23:45.240 --> 23:46.120
You'll be fine.

23:46.320 --> 23:48.400
With Aunt gone, I'm finally free.

23:48.680 --> 23:50.000
In your dreams.

23:50.040 --> 23:50.760
Let me tell you,

23:50.760 --> 23:53.220
I've made a study plan for your new semester.

23:53.600 --> 23:54.800
Starting today,

23:54.800 --> 23:56.720
your tablet time is cut in half.

23:57.960 --> 23:58.360
Mom.

23:58.400 --> 24:00.560
Why are you becoming exactly like Aunt?

24:00.560 --> 24:02.000
What do you mean 'like Aunt'?

24:02.000 --> 24:03.440
I spoiled you too much before.

24:03.440 --> 24:04.120
You know?

24:04.520 --> 24:06.040
Sis, please help me.

24:06.080 --> 24:06.680
Help you with what?

24:06.680 --> 24:07.880
I'm leaving, Aunt.

24:08.480 --> 24:09.940
I'll walk you downstairs.

24:10.280 --> 24:12.410
No need. I'm going to the antique shop.

24:12.920 --> 24:13.760
Got it. Go ahead.

24:13.760 --> 24:16.020
Sis, say hello to Brother-in-Law for me.

24:16.080 --> 24:17.880
What are you talking about, kid?

24:18.840 --> 24:19.900
Be safe on your way.

24:23.040 --> 24:24.570
How is it? Does it look good?

24:26.040 --> 24:28.040
I didn't expect you to work here too.

24:28.120 --> 24:28.920
Of course.

24:29.120 --> 24:31.040
I'm a part-time guide here now.

24:31.360 --> 24:32.000
After school starts,

24:32.000 --> 24:33.720
I only need to come twice a week.

24:33.720 --> 24:35.580
We will be colleagues from now on.

24:36.120 --> 24:37.120
Great guide Qi Yi,

24:37.400 --> 24:39.260
please take care of me from now on.

24:40.000 --> 24:42.130
Then please take care of me from now on.

24:44.320 --> 24:46.320
Anyway, I'm your senior now.

24:46.400 --> 24:47.960
If you encounter any problems later,

24:47.960 --> 24:49.820
you must humbly ask me for advice.

24:50.920 --> 24:51.780
Hello, senior.

24:52.680 --> 24:53.410
Time to work.

24:53.560 --> 24:54.560
Okay, senior.

24:55.960 --> 24:56.960
Boss, we're back.

24:58.600 --> 24:59.160
You're back.

24:59.160 --> 24:59.840
Boss.

25:00.520 --> 25:01.720
You're finally back.

25:01.720 --> 25:02.920
Let me introduce you.

25:02.920 --> 25:04.580
This is my college classmate,

25:04.600 --> 25:05.530
artist Lao Shen.

25:06.120 --> 25:06.680
Hello.

25:06.680 --> 25:07.940
How was your vacation?

25:19.520 --> 25:20.250
Apprentice.

25:20.440 --> 25:22.040
You came back so early today.

25:22.760 --> 25:23.560
Have you been drinking?

25:23.560 --> 25:24.920
No.

25:26.600 --> 25:27.960
I drank some tea.

25:28.000 --> 25:28.360
I,

25:29.400 --> 25:30.860
the sauce-flavored type.

25:31.640 --> 25:32.000
I,

25:32.040 --> 25:34.040
this is my only hobby.

25:34.400 --> 25:36.160
Just let me have a sip.

25:36.320 --> 25:37.240
Just one sip.

25:37.360 --> 25:38.720
Did you smoke again last night?

25:38.720 --> 25:41.040
I didn't smoke. Where would I get cigarettes?

25:41.040 --> 25:42.170
I smelled the smoke.

25:42.520 --> 25:43.560
That, yesterday,

25:43.680 --> 25:44.440
that was mosquito repellent.

25:44.440 --> 25:46.040
I lit some, that's the smell.

25:46.520 --> 25:47.640
The doctor said

25:47.920 --> 25:48.640
smoking

25:48.800 --> 25:49.600
and drinking,

25:49.640 --> 25:50.700
I have to quit both.

25:53.640 --> 25:54.520
Hurry up. Let me teach you.

25:54.520 --> 25:55.360
No.

25:55.360 --> 25:56.420
Hold out your hand.

25:56.480 --> 25:57.720
It's really fun.

25:57.720 --> 25:57.840
Take it away. I don't want it.

25:57.840 --> 25:59.440
Take it away. I don't want it.

26:00.160 --> 26:00.640
Xiaoyi,

26:00.960 --> 26:02.960
let me show you a new trick I learned.

26:06.000 --> 26:06.440
Isn't it amazing?

26:06.440 --> 26:07.920
That's incredible!

26:08.920 --> 26:09.450
Xiaocen.

26:10.320 --> 26:10.880
Xu Xiao.

26:12.360 --> 26:13.220
Are you hungry?

26:13.360 --> 26:13.890
Let's go.

26:26.160 --> 26:27.880
Alright, that's it for today's livestream.

26:27.880 --> 26:29.080
Thank you, everyone.

26:33.720 --> 26:34.320
Xia Qing,

26:34.760 --> 26:36.220
your work is so beautiful.

26:36.800 --> 26:38.130
Thank you for liking it.

26:38.160 --> 26:39.760
Our brand name is Banlan.

26:40.000 --> 26:41.400
We hope you can follow us.

26:42.120 --> 26:43.400
Xia Qing, Jing,

26:43.600 --> 26:45.320
your works are so popular.

26:45.520 --> 26:47.000
Why don't you consider opening a store

26:47.000 --> 26:48.400
to expand your business?

26:48.400 --> 26:49.640
Every time I want to buy more,

26:49.640 --> 26:50.520
they are all sold out.

26:50.520 --> 26:52.640
We don't have such plans yet.

26:53.160 --> 26:54.760
We still want to take it slow

26:55.200 --> 26:58.000
to accumulate experience and strength bit by bit.

26:58.480 --> 26:59.240
Xia Qing,

26:59.320 --> 27:00.800
your craftsmanship is really unique.

27:00.800 --> 27:01.760
Who taught you?

27:04.640 --> 27:06.300
I have a group of good friends.

27:10.520 --> 27:11.560
Don't you think so?

27:11.560 --> 27:12.000
Mom,

27:12.080 --> 27:12.920
have some tea.

27:15.280 --> 27:17.200
First loading, second firing, and third cooling.

27:17.200 --> 27:18.000
Master said so.

27:18.000 --> 27:20.000
The most crucial parts of firing a kiln are loading,

27:20.000 --> 27:20.800
temperature control,

27:20.800 --> 27:22.280
and the proper cooling time.

27:22.280 --> 27:22.840
Got it?

27:35.840 --> 27:37.000
When the wind stops,

27:37.360 --> 27:39.040
the leaves will fall.

27:39.960 --> 27:41.200
Falling here,

27:41.600 --> 27:43.460
the leaves have found their home.

28:10.240 --> 28:10.840
Xiaocen.

28:12.240 --> 28:12.760
Coming.
